The paper deals with the problem of index coding, which is a well-studied problem in information theory (cs.IT). The focus is on the multi-sender case, which involves distributed coding and communication (cs.NI, cs.DC). The proposed solution involves cooperative coding, which is a topic in both information theory and computer networks (cs.SI, cs.CC).
